# Terraform
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
crash.log
crash.*.log
# .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored - it should be committed
# so CI and local runs resolve the same provider versions.

# Secrets / local env
*.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
